snippet.title: The X-Files: Resist or Serve | PS2 | 2004 | Video Game US Trailer (2) | LQ/OGR
snippet.description:
US Trailer for the The X-Files: Resist or Serve video game, based on the X-Files TV series.

Published in United States by Vivendi Universal Games in 2004 for PlayStation 2
